content.rendered:
Directed by Renuka Shahane

Written by Renuka Shahane

Cast Kajol(Anuradha Apte). Tanvi Azmi(Nayantara Apte). Mithila Palkar(Masha). Kunaal Roy Kapur(Milan Upadhyay). Vaibhav Tatwawadi(Robindro (as Vaibhav Tatwawaadi)). Kanwaljeet Singh(Bhaskar Raina (as Kanwaljit Singh)). Manav Gohil(Raghav). Shweta Mehendale(Nayan (Young) (as Sweta Mehendale)). Piyush Ranade(Vinayak (Young Baba)). Rajani Welankar(Aaji (Nayan’s Mother-in-Law)). Antara Deshpande(Young Anu). Ayush Joshi(Young Robindro). Harsha Gupte(Vimal Maushi). Sheetal Shukla(Kumud Aatya). Deepak Kripalani(Dr. Mayekar (as Deepak Kriplani)). Reshma Shetty(Main Nurse). Arha Mahajan(Little Anu). Shivansh Shukla(Little Robindro). Sukanya Dhanda(Mummyji (Deepak’s Mother) (as Sukanya Danda)). Nishank Verma(Vikramaditya). Ashok Kelkar(Vinayak (Old Baba)). Sharavan Borana(Deepak). Richard John Lovatt(Dimitri (Anu’s Russian Boyfriend) (as Richard Lovatt)). Rahim Pirani(Shantanu (Anu’s Pa)). Apurva Dani(Odissi Dancer). Mugdha Karnik(Femal Journalist 1 Outside Hospital). Anirudh Nayar(Male Journalist 1 Outside Hospital). Surabhi Bhave(Mrs. Bapat (Class Teacher)). Sonali Sharmistha Mohanty(Nurse 1 (as Sonali Mohanty)). Mayuri Zore(Nurse 2). Ashish Tyagi(Nayan’s Guest). Xylan Fernandes(Little Anu’s Classmate (Boy)). Kimaya Pathak(Little Masha). Basant Mody(Old Patriarch). Manasi Naik(Anchor). Jash Mahetalia(Deepak’s Cousin). Tawhid Rike Zaman(Arman)

Language Hindi

Producers. Girish Balan. Parag Desai. Ajay Devgn. Deepak Dhar. Dyuti Geete. Sapna Malhotra. Rishi Negi. Kumar Mangat Pathak. Chaunce Philipose. Amit Sidana. Malhotra P. Siddharth.

Production Ajay Devgn Films.. Alchemy Productons. Banijay Asia
